==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sustentative
<hw>Sus"ten*ta*tive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Adapted to
sustain, strengthen, or corroborate; <as>as, <ex>sustentative</ex>
citations or quotations</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Sustentative functions</b></col> <fld>(Physiol.)</fld>,
<cd>those functions of the body which affect its material composition
and thus determine its mass.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sustention</ent>⟦br⟧
